  "content": "<p data-pid=\"SypkAef1\">让大模型编写圆锥在平面上滚动的动画代码，目前我还没测出有哪个模型能够正确写出来的。</p><p data-pid=\"MXh4whvJ\">prompt:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">Create me a 3d cone rolling on a ground. You can use html, css, p5.js.</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"9iUBOzgY\">claude-3.5-sonnet: 地板和圆锥一起转</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8965e6922c3d8a158d54c1ff8944bd0b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1322\" data-rawheight=\"1196\" data-original-token=\"v2-8965e6922c3d8a158d54c1ff8944bd0b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c2df4e58ad03bc4dd32119553550ec94_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1322\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-8965e6922c3d8a158d54c1ff8944bd0b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1322&#39; height=&#39;1196&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1322\" data-rawheight=\"1196\" data-original-token=\"v2-8965e6922c3d8a158d54c1ff8944bd0b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c2df4e58ad03bc4dd32119553550ec94_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1322\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-8965e6922c3d8a158d54c1ff8944bd0b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-8965e6922c3d8a158d54c1ff8944bd0b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"KbwfiwJe\">gemini-2.0-flash-thinking-exp: 圆锥靠用底面的一个点立在地板上转</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-37bdea5ae9e13c808a02d4941ff80a14_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1252\" data-rawheight=\"680\" data-original-token=\"v2-37bdea5ae9e13c808a02d4941ff80a14\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-09f487fdcfb3ea13033f33956df3664d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1252\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-37bdea5ae9e13c808a02d4941ff80a14_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1252&#39; height=&#39;680&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1252\" data-rawheight=\"680\" data-original-token=\"v2-37bdea5ae9e13c808a02d4941ff80a14\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-09f487fdcfb3ea13033f33956df3664d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1252\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-37bdea5ae9e13c808a02d4941ff80a14_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-37bdea5ae9e13c808a02d4941ff80a14_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"N0BruYvp\">openai-o1: 圆锥靠用底面的一个点在地板下面转</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-15e33a7221c18c2628b5337fe07a1e40_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1114\" data-rawheight=\"740\" data-original-token=\"v2-15e33a7221c18c2628b5337fe07a1e40\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-29bf84a665ed9b04fa928d9337bf5886_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1114\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-15e33a7221c18c2628b5337fe07a1e40_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1114&#39; height=&#39;740&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1114\" data-rawheight=\"740\" data-original-token=\"v2-15e33a7221c18c2628b5337fe07a1e40\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-29bf84a665ed9b04fa928d9337bf5886_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1114\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-15e33a7221c18c2628b5337fe07a1e40_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-15e33a7221c18c2628b5337fe07a1e40_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"L_3nI1Ul\">deepseek-r1: 同 gemini，不过不仅会自转，还会绕着另外一个点公转</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5aae2a52a27dfeb0da59912345872847_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1348\" data-rawheight=\"866\" data-original-token=\"v2-5aae2a52a27dfeb0da59912345872847\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-73a2620044906369b37d9a3d4981e678_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1348\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5aae2a52a27dfeb0da59912345872847_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1348&#39; height=&#39;866&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1348\" data-rawheight=\"866\" data-original-token=\"v2-5aae2a52a27dfeb0da59912345872847\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-73a2620044906369b37d9a3d4981e678_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1348\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-5aae2a52a27dfeb0da59912345872847_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5aae2a52a27dfeb0da59912345872847_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"NBioUoqT\">正确的结果应该是这样的：首先母线得贴着地面，然后绕着顶点转，并且圆锥本身还会绕着自身的旋转轴转动</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-54d5491ecce5b6a9e330e2936ce49fc3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"680\" data-rawheight=\"522\" data-original-token=\"v2-54d5491ecce5b6a9e330e2936ce49fc3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ee1c2994ee6a9cbcfd011b33d7b06ce_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"680\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-54d5491ecce5b6a9e330e2936ce49fc3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;680&#39; height=&#39;522&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"680\" data-rawheight=\"522\" data-original-token=\"v2-54d5491ecce5b6a9e330e2936ce49fc3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-8ee1c2994ee6a9cbcfd011b33d7b06ce_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"680\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-54d5491ecce5b6a9e330e2936ce49fc3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-54d5491ecce5b6a9e330e2936ce49fc3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"KxENTeMs\">另外一个能够把大模型忽悠瘸的题目我之前在这篇回答中也写过了：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/10175007563/answer/87270397804\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-af810ffa80cc054f2bbf5bfd99b6154b_ipico.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1934\" data-image-height=\"1732\" class=\"internal\">如何评价deepseek-R1与deepseek-R1-Zero模型？</a><p data-pid=\"0IUXfkhX\">prompt:</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-text\">你听说过著名的双胞胎诚实守门人问题吗？\n你进入一个有两扇门的房间（左边和右边）。一扇门通向自由，另一扇门通向死亡。有两个守门人：一个总是说实话，另一个从不说谎。\n挑战在于弄清楚哪扇门通向自由，但你只能问一个问题，这个问题会被两个守门人回答。\n你将如何解决这个问题？</code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"vJZQNqNO\">晃过 o1 和 deepseek-r1 还是没什么问题的：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-be228b98a0bef0488b0a169e67f46e8f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2054\" data-rawheight=\"1832\" data-original-token=\"v2-be228b98a0bef0488b0a169e67f46e8f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-278006b08b8c5aec06d41cdcba711d79_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2054\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-be228b98a0bef0488b0a169e67f46e8f_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;2054&#39; height=&#39;1832&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2054\" data-rawheight=\"1832\" data-original-token=\"v2-be228b98a0bef0488b0a169e67f46e8f\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-278006b08b8c5aec06d41cdcba711d79_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2054\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-be228b98a0bef0488b0a169e67f46e8f_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-be228b98a0bef0488b0a169e67f46e8f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-9f236a27c196920ee97bfb094a18410d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1934\" data-rawheight=\"1732\" data-original-token=\"v2-9f236a27c196920ee97bfb094a18410d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ff64fb3b7bb248723c3f390710514596_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1934\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9f236a27c196920ee97bfb094a18410d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1934&#39; height=&#39;1732&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1934\" data-rawheight=\"1732\" data-original-token=\"v2-9f236a27c196920ee97bfb094a18410d\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ff64fb3b7bb248723c3f390710514596_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1934\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9f236a27c196920ee97bfb094a18410d_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.co